  "name": "RPlog_Masquerade_Ball_A_Night_on_Yavin",
  "title": "Masquerade Ball: A Night on Yavin",
  "summary": "The Wampa Lounge aboard the Angry Rancor is transformed into a jungle-themed venue for a costumed masquerade ball set on Yavin. This index entry establishes the setting and catalogues the night's elaborate disguises, from the prize-winning Massassi-totem costume of Ramyxth and the raven-haired Lepidoptera to the Lethan Twi'lek Ka'una as a body-painted striped cat. A parade of other guests appear in costume, a tiki torch, a piranha beetle, a Rebel pilot, the Count, a Serenella imposter, a Hoojib, a Wookiee, a Ranphyx, and the bird-feathered Birdie, with Solon Halwinder and Kyrin attending uncostumed. The full role-play is split across five linked parts transcluded here, capturing the evening's masked revelry in detail.",
